Title : The New Girls
Text : {{notability|books|date=April 2014}}
{{Italic title}}
'''''The New Girls''''' is a 1979 novel by American author [[Beth Gutcheon]].  The novel drew loosely upon the author's own experience of the cruel and rarified atmosphere of elite boarding schools, and was well received by critics.<ref>https://www.harpercollins.com/web-sampler/9780060977023</ref>

